content:
This cutie pie is Moe. Check out his custom made casts!
(Swipe to see more pics)
Kate Doyle, a Vet Tech, in Perth, Australia, creates color custom casts in her spare time to help owners feel better after their pets undergo big surgeries. She says it makes them smile every time.
Kate says Moe was a neglected dog when he was brought to her. His leg was fractured, he had a broken pelvis and was very malnourished. Unfortunately, after 2 weeks in the splint and physical therapy, Moe had to have his leg amputated. But the good news is, Moe is safe and now has a forever home with Kate!! (Photo credit: @cute_moonbear) #dogsofinstagram #dogs #cutie #vettech #veterinarian #puppy
